# Tiling
Control Shift Left :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 99.9%} {MoveTo 00 00 Left}
Control Shift Right :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 99.9%} {MoveTo 00 00 Right}
Control Shift Up :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 100% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Up}
#Control Shift Up :Maximize
Control Shift Down :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 100% 50%} {MoveTo 00 00 Bottom}







